{
  "stem": "15610.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We have one room.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the kitchen was shared with three families.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was-- was not too bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could exist there if they leave us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they liquidate the ghetto, and everybody has to go to the concentration camp in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this was terrible day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Be without mother and brother, and now you have to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Leave everything, just take something in your two hands and go to a concentration camp, which was built on a cemetery.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this was terrible, but what you can do?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they'd been talking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People had been talking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the commandant was Amon Goeth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't know how terrible he is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then we find out when we move in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when we came there, it was a cemetery, so they gave us--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we walked there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not so far.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not so far from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They give us hammer in the hands and tell us to break the stones, the gravestones, and make street from it, roads, because it was dirty roads.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was Jewish cemetery there where they created the-- the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Amon Goeth, he was our commandant, and he'd been shooting people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you can imagine what's-- how scary place it could get there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First, we'd been breaking the stones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then one group they took and told us we're going to a brush factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To a brush factory.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we worked there in the brush-- I worked there in the brush factory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All kind of brushes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Cleaning dresses, coats, for shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All kind of brushes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There in the-- in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But what was bad there, that there was window in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
